body:
Hey,

I am Tatqna from Bulgaria and i want to invite u guys to enjoy my streams! In my Stream i will talk mostly english but its also fine to ask me questions in Bulgarian. I am 15 years old and like to do Cosplays, for example from my favorite Champion Ahri as u can see very often in the stream :) I am currently in Platinum and mostly like to play Support and MIdlane.
I mostly stream in the evening and hope we can meet very soon in my stream !
